              Business formation, contracts, mergers & acquisitions, corporate
              governance, and compliance matters.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Business entity formation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Mergers & acquisitions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Contract negotiation & drafting</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Practice Area 2 -->
          <div
            class="group p-8 bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-slate-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
              Civil Litigation
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Experienced trial attorneys representing clients in complex civil
              disputes, commercial litigation, and appeals.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Commercial disputes</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Contract disputes</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Appeals & post-trial motions</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Practice Area 3 -->
          <div
            class="group p-8 bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-slate-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
